SYNOPSIS
  creator
  creator <object>

DESCRIPTION
  This command returns some information about the creators of the room
  you are in (first form) or about the specified <object> (second form).

  The <object> is searched first in the environment, then in your
  inventory. Use the keyword 'my' or adjectives to unambigously 
  specify an object.

EXAMPLES
  Getting information about the current room:
    creator
    creator room
    
  Getting information about some objects:
    creator bag
    creator my sword
    creator sword in stone

SEE ALSO
  bug, idea, laud, typo, syntax
